{"lastModified":1751633102496,"uri":"c::7580644653::vessel::d5cbaba4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sicily, Corsica, Italy, Sardinia, Marseille, France, Monaco\n\n\nLady Amanda refitted 2021 and launched in 2006, a 30-metre Couach offering the best selection of onboard toys.  She is a premium charter vessel, looks amazing and has one of the most welcoming crews. \n\nLady Amanda’s impressive leisure and entertaining facilities have made her a well-known and popular fixture on the charter scene. Her owner is particularly passionate about watersports, therefore Lady Amanda boasts a selection of toys better than that of many 45-metre yachts. These include a 4,6metre tender, a 5-metre slide, a Fliteboard AIR 175litre, a FlyBoard, Jetsurf, an ocean pool with jellyfish protection net, a golfing pad with biodegradable balls, a balloon blast, a crane swing, PWC, seabobs, immotor electric scooter, an SJ pro SUP package, paddleboards, snorkelling and fishing equipment, waterskis, wakeboards, a wakeskate and a doughnut amongst others. There is also a Mavic pro platinum air drone and a Power Ray power vision sub drone to immortalise the guest experience.  As an RYA approved school for jetskis, her crew are commited to curating safe, high-quality experiences on the water.\n\nLady Amanda is able to accommodate 10 guests in four ensuite cabins, across a full beam master suite, a queen and two doubles with a Pullman each. The classic interior from Franck Reynaud is light and inviting, with calming neutral whites and polished woods the dominant theme. A comfortable saloon with easy access to the outdoors creates a sociable space. The yacht also boasts impressive outdoor deck space that includes several lounging and dining areas across the aft deck, foredeck and large flybridge, and sun pads on the foredeck and a Jacuzzi on the flybridge. \n\nWith an impressive cruising speed of 22-26 knots, Lady Amanda is able to cruise between locations in comfort and style, enabling guests to experience a large area of coastline in a short space of time, perfect for those who want to explore places ashore as well as enjoy the yacht’s amenities.  \n\nA wonderful crew of four ensures smooth running and a memorable guest experience. Although still young, captain Ashley has accumulated over 14 years’ experience in the yachting industry already, across multiple boats up to 60-metres. Fastidious in his approach to onboard welfare and safety, Lady Amanda is a first class charter yacht. Captain Ashley himself says: “The safety and training of this crew and vessel are only matched by the amount of fun and games offered to the guests on board.”\n\nThe yacht is currently in Cannes, France and is available to charter in the Western Mediterranean, and Lady Amanda now accepts Bitcoin for charter fees, so contact your broker today for more information! \n\n“Lady Amanda’s impressive leisure and entertaining facilities have made her a well-known and popular fixture on the charter scene\"","blueprint":{"name":"LADY AMANDA","images":["/media/media::image::c::7580644653::vessel::d5cbaba4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::56a36730-fda3-11ee-b883-d3dabf68e691.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644653::vessel::d5cbaba4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6b5170a0-fda3-11ee-b883-d3dabf68e691.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644653::vessel::d5cbaba4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6b52d030-fda3-11ee-b883-d3dabf68e691.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644653::vessel::d5cbaba4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a1ca4b70-fda3-11ee-b883-d3dabf68e691.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644653::vessel::d5cbaba4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a1cac0a0-fda3-11ee-b883-d3dabf68e691.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644653::vessel::d5cbaba4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a1c8ebe0-fda3-11ee-b883-d3dabf68e691.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::im